Punjab
Oct 12, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			A 9-year-old-girl was allegedly raped by a youth in Sirhind area of the district.

On October 10, 24-year-old Gurpreet Singh came to the home of the victim and took her away on his bicycle, according to the complaint lodged by the mother of the girl.

When she did not return home, her family members started searching and found her near a canal on the outskirts of the village, police said.

The youth fled from the scene after raping the class v girl.

Police is carrying out searches to nab the accused.

